data.description: Open concept ranch with over 1300 SQFT. The kitchen offers spacious cabinets and various counter space and an island. The continuity between the kitchen and living room provides a perfect space for entertaining. There are three bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The master bedroom provides access to the porch and also contains a large walk-in closet. House also features a doggy door in the living room to allow for easy access for pets to the outside alcove area. Large fenced-in backyard with a tree house perfect for summer events.
